race.comment: MISS MANAUDOU (6) finished in the minors last start over the 407m at this track but ran a quick 23.77 last start. Should be in this for a long way. HUDSON RIVERLINE (8) boasts a strong record this journey with five wins and seven minors from 15 tries. Placed last time (23.95) at this track in a Grade 3/4, finishing third and beaten 4.5 lengths. Among the main chances. DREAM DESIGN (2) is in the mix after placing last time out. Something for the Multiples: ASTON CHEROKEE (3)
